originalText.text: Tried to get in my apartment and was locked out. Key worked for the building but this morning maintenance had shown up to fix an issue and now I can’t get in. Tried calling the maintenance hotline and got treated like they didn’t care. The on call maintenance person finally called and sounded drunk and didn’t have a master key. Honestly pitiful service for when you get locked out.
